ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolSPP = Type 47-S pistol holster rig
    .desc = The Type 47-S is the standard load-bearing equipment of the SPP. It consists of a modular belt with various clips. This version has a holster assembly that allows one to carry the most common pistols. It also contains side pouches that can store most pistol magazines.
