ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolParaCustom = paramarine custom load-bearing rig
    .desc = A modified RCM Paramarine belt featuring a black leather holster with gold inlay, a large utility pouch, and several smaller compartments provide ample space for extra ammunition and field essentials — standard gear for Paramarines dropping into hostile territory.
